::Killfest::

Killfest frowns, looking around at all the bots saddened by KitKat's 
death. He could understand a bit of regret at losing a leader, but 
this? This wasn't Predacon.

"I think we should put her in cryo storage for now," he says, nodding 
to Demise. Demise walks to KitKat and lifts her in one of his huge 
clawed hands.

"KitKat shall be honored," he says, looking at DarkMouse, "But can we 
get on with the codes?"
